= Installation =
== Whonix-Gateway TemplateVM Binary Install ==
'''1. Launch Dom0 Terminal'''

In Dom0 -> Application Launcher Menu -> System Tools:

* Click on the "Konsole (Terminal)" app to launch it.

'''2. Install Whonix-Gateway TemplateVM'''

In Dom0 -> Terminal:

* Input command: <code>sudo qubes-dom0-update --enablerepo=qubes-templates-community qubes-template-whonix-gw-experimental</code>

== Whonix-Workstation TemplateVM Binary Install ==
'''1. Launch Dom0 Terminal'''

In Dom0 -> Application Launcher Menu -> System Tools:

* Click on the "Konsole (Terminal)" app to launch it.

'''2. Increase Update Size'''

The Gnome version of the Whonix-Workstation TemplateVM may be too large and will you need to increase the allowed update size to accommodate installing it.

In Dom0 -> Terminal:

* Input command:<br /> <code>export UPDATES_MAX_BYTES=$[ 4 * 1024 ** 3 ]</code>

'''3. Install Whonix-Workstation TemplateVM'''

In Dom0 -> Terminal:

* Input command:<br /> <code>sudo qubes-dom0-update --enablerepo=qubes-templates-community qubes-template-whonix-ws</code>

OR, to install Workstation with complete Gnome applications that are installed in Qubes Fedora templates:<br /> 
For Gnome, read security notes on [[Other Desktop Environments]].

* Input command:<br /> <code>sudo qubes-dom0-update --enablerepo=qubes-templates-community qubes-template-whonix-ws-gnome</code>

